{"tid":2044952,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"又長一歲！「地表最犯規AV」波多野結衣露點健身…網笑翻","createTime":"2020-05-31T12:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T13:17:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e29f5401f5dfb140dc5c5fca3bbda449173950","tid":2044952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"有「暗黑林志玲」之稱的日本AV女優波多野結衣，同時也是知名度最高的S級女優之一，上星期波多野結衣剛度過其32歲生日，近日因為武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒、COVID-19）肆虐，她沒能舉辦慶生活動與粉絲面對面，不過在經紀事務所仍收到大量全球各地粉絲所贈的生日禮物，連日來她都在社群平台IG拍照大曬禮物。<br />\n<br />\n而波多野結衣雖32歲外型仍相當稚嫩，入行12年依然擁高人氣，她也趁不用開工期間狂跑健身房，只見波多野結衣竟赤膊著上半身「露兩點」，原來她搞笑套上「大隻佬」的露點猛男背心，還擺出舉二頭肌的動作，笑翻網友們。<br />\n<br />\n不少粉絲看了也不禁留言「很難想像波多野變成六塊腹肌大隻佬」、「要是練成這樣太恐怖了吧？」、「練特殊技練出來的？」也有人歪樓說：「在家裡絕對是這樣赤膊！」、「在胸肌上流著汗」"},{"pid":"6d7c89802d9caa14c18f395f587c763cb5cb9bfd","tid":2044952,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2584771-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2584771-XXL.jpg&h=14376038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼日前波多野結衣貼健身房穿露點猛男背心。（圖／翻攝自波多野結衣推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2584773-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2584773-XXL.jpg&h=f80cfea7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf188d7f95720321110d117ba4a331c6c35869ea","tid":2044952,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2584770-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2584770-XXL.jpg&h=8f922c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「暗黑林志玲」之稱的波多野結衣又長一歲。（圖／翻攝自波多野結衣推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2584777-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2584777-XXL.jpg&h=fb0ac5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲波多野結衣雖32歲樣貌仍稚嫩。（圖／翻攝自波多野結衣推特）"},{"pid":"3e20497345bc68eda483a100cb1d5e305165439b","tid":2044952,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇佢啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我從來唔睇AV因為我有彩瑛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc985afcd063271c09f2d322d7674eddba226c76","tid":2044952,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e20497345bc68eda483a100cb1d5e305165439b","tid":2044952,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇佢啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我從來唔睇AV因為我有彩瑛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"彩瑛已嫁樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd24ea702afee7ed331f4462f51c0d62fd74f7ad","tid":2044952,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e20497345bc68eda483a100cb1d5e305165439b","tid":2044952,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇佢啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"